<p><b>Adrian Frutiger</b> (born May 24, <a href="/wiki/1928" title="1928">1928</a>) is one of the prominent typeface designers of the twentieth century, who continues influencing the direction of digital typography in the twenty-first century; he is best known for creating the typefaces <a href="/wiki/Univers" title="Univers">Univers</a> and <a href="/wiki/Frutiger" title="Frutiger">Frutiger</a>.</p>
